  <scopecontent id="aspace_41697f02e036b32471f3f3d18efc834a">
    <head>COLLECTION DESCRIPTION</head>
<p>Correspondence, accounts, receipts, deeds (including deeds for the sale of slaves), wills, inventory, and other papers pertaining to land transactions and other activities of the van Schaick family, including Anna, Anthony, Christina, Gerrit, Jacob, John, Henry, and Gerard van Schaick. Also, a map for the village of Oswego, New York.</p>  </scopecontent>
