lect, the powder missed the boat.</unittitle><unitdate calendar="gregorian" era="ce" normal="1771/1771">1771</unitdate><container id="aspace_28fd0a07be2adce280860355b513bb20" label="Mixed Materials [31924064926607]" type="box">1</container><container id="aspace_f8c69e8fd43d2c2466a303b84ee2a50e" parent="aspace_28fd0a07be2adce280860355b513bb20" type="folder">3</container></did></c03><c03 id="aspace_050ddac1f90b6c3a6cb8d42e40131d57" level="item"><did><unittitle>1771 - from Thomas Harris - Mar.</unittitle><unitdate calendar="gregorian" era="ce" normal="1771/1771">1771</unitdate><container id="aspace_d23cc1ffb2beb014a9e328ee0b9570b9" label="Mixed Materials [31924064926607]" type="box">1</container><container id="aspace_51298c54416a6fa4041f9dc983c32e7f" parent="aspace_d23cc1ffb2beb014a9e328ee0b9570b9" type="folder">3</container></did></c03><c03 id="aspace_130dae7ed2c2a79e4759cedd740cf8c1" level="item"><did><unittitle>1771 - from Pink van der Hayden, London - speaks of the death of Thomas Harris - "after a short illness of a violent fever"</unittitle><unitdate calendar="gregorian" era="ce" normal="1771/1771">1771</unitdate><container id="aspace_5a179ed294ba6c0b2138529f2a537a82" label="Mixed Materials [31924064926607]" type="box">1</container><container id="aspace_e91d6a6882bfe5b59511fc6d031d50da" parent="aspace_5a179ed294ba6c0b2138529f2a537a82" type="folder">3</container></did></c03><c03 id="aspace_b35f1f57c7774526ef58f8162b4ee4ed" level="item"><did><unittitle>1775 - copy of a letter from John Blackburn, London - quotes prices of wheat, flour.</unittitle><unitdate calendar="gregorian" era="ce" normal="1775/1775">1775</unitdate><container id="aspace_840d056566c9a4d5c28e12be383a4e6d" label="Mixed Materials [31924064926607]" type="box">1</container><container id="aspace_b5283601b0ff96c1cc93b65b9c823636" parent="aspace_840d056566c9a4d5c28e12be383a4e6d" type="folder">3</container></did></c03></c02><c02 id="aspace_5358199c378be67656ddec5899aa5c31" level="item"><did><unittitle>1 